A small child joyfully riding on the back of a massive, colorful ceramic tiger statue in a whimsical overgrown garden setting, surrounded by fantastical mythological sculptures covered in moss and vines, golden afternoon sunlight filtering through tropical trees, the tiger painted in vibrant oranges, greens and golds with exaggerated folk art patterns, Studio Ghibli animation style with soft watercolor textures, dreamy atmosphere, lush Singapore vegetation, crumbling ornate pillars and faded painted dragons visible in the background, sense of faded grandeur mixed with childhood wonder and adventure.
